 face of waves of cyber harassment she has suffered since the opening ceremony: threats of death, torture, rape, antisemitic, homophobic, sexist and fatphobic insults.\", \"from\": 5003, \"to\": 5328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5003, \"end\": 5009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9991899349912541, \"rank\": 0.0005860724746291363, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 5022, \"end\": 5036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SOS_Homophobie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SOS homophobie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SOS_Homophobie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SOS_Homophobie\"}, {\"begin\": 5141, \"end\": 5154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"score\": 0.9999897744159937, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Barbara Butch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the following statement\", \"from\": 5044, \"to\": 5067}, {\"ngram\": \"the wake\", \"from\": 5071, \"to\": 5079}, {\"ngram\": \"Butch's complaint\", \"from\": 5083, \"to\": 5100}, {\"ngram\": \"SOS homophobie\", \"from\": 5103, \"to\": 5117}, {\"ngram\": \"total support\", \"from\": 5124, \"to\": 5137}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 5158, \"to\": 5166}, {\"ngram\": \"waves\", \"from\": 5170, \"to\": 5175}, {\"ngram\": \"cyber harassment\", \"from\": 5179, \"to\": 5195}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 5219, \"to\": 5239}, {\"ngram\": \"threats\", \"from\": 5241, \"to\": 5248}, {\"ngram\": \"death\", \"from\": 5252, \"to\": 5257}, {\"ngram\": \"torture, rape, antisemitic, homophobic, sexist and fatphobic insults\", \"from\": 5259, \"to\": 5327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hatred will not pass.\\\"\", \"from\": 5329, \"to\": 5351, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hatred\", \"from\": 5329, \"to\": 5335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Butch performed at the opening ceremony on Friday 26 July, alongside dancers and drag artists like Nicky Doll and Paloma, in a tableau entitled \\\"Festivit\\u00e9\\\".\", \"from\": 5353, \"to\": 5509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5467, \"end\": 5473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"score\": 0.999999545057666, \"rank\": 4.546030958019067e-07, \"text\": \"Paloma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Butch\", \"from\": 5353, \"to\": 5358}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 5372, \"to\": 5392}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 5396, \"to\": 5402}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 5406, \"to\": 5410}, {\"ngram\": \"dancers\", \"from\": 5422, \"to\": 5429}, {\"ngram\": \"drag artists\", \"from\": 5434, \"to\": 5446}, {\"ngram\": \"Nicky Doll\", \"from\": 5452, \"to\": 5462}, {\"ngram\": \"a tableau\", \"from\": 5478, \"to\": 5487}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Festivit\\u00e9\", \"from\": 5497, \"to\": 5507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to its detractors, this sequence is a parody of Leonardo da Vinci's \\\"The Last Supper\\\", and it has caused quite the ruckus.\", \"from\": 5511, \"to\": 5643, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5569, \"end\": 5586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.86997061860117e-22, \"text\": \"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its detractors\", \"from\": 5524, \"to\": 5538}, {\"ngram\": \"this sequence\", \"from\": 5540, \"to\": 5553}, {\"ngram\": \"a parody\", \"from\": 5557, \"to\": 5565}, {\"ngram\": \"quite the ruckus\", \"from\": 5626, \"to\": 5642}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The French Bishops' Conference (CEF) deplored \\\"scenes of derision and mockery of Christianity\\\" - a sentiment echoed by Russian Foreign Ministry spokesperson Maria Zakharova.\", \"from\": 5645, \"to\": 5818, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5677, \"end\": 5680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Expeditionary_Force\", \"score\": 0.9994039989522889, \"rank\": 0.0005963564769379811, \"text\": \"CEF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Expeditionary_Force\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Expeditionary_Force\"}, {\"begin\": 5726, \"end\": 5738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999990248880046, \"rank\": 9.737873191006328e-07, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 5764, \"end\": 5788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs_(Russia)\", \"score\": 0.999999999875854, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Russian Foreign Ministry\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs_(Russia)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs_(Russia)\"}, {\"begin\": 5802, \"end\": 5817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maria_Zakharova\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maria Zakharova\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maria_Zakharova\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maria_Zakharova\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The French Bishops' Conference\", \"from\": 5645, \"to\": 5675}, {\"ngram\": \"scenes\", \"from\": 5692, \"to\": 5698}, {\"ngram\": \"derision\", \"from\": 5702, \"to\": 5710}, {\"ngram\": \"mockery\", \"from\": 5715, \"to\": 5722}, {\"ngram\"