essage\", \"from\": 6012, \"to\": 6036}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then there is Andrew Tate, the controversial media personality awaiting trial on charges of human trafficking, rape and forming a criminal gang to sexually exploit women...\", \"from\": 6040, \"to\": 6212, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6061, \"end\": 6065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\", \"score\": 0.9997170215751676, \"rank\": 0.0002829473240008194, \"text\": \"Tate\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the controversial media personality\", \"from\": 6067, \"to\": 6102}, {\"ngram\": \"trial\", \"from\": 6112, \"to\": 6117}, {\"ngram\": \"charges\", \"from\": 6121, \"to\": 6128}, {\"ngram\": \"human trafficking\", \"from\": 6132, \"to\": 6149}, {\"ngram\": \"rape\", \"from\": 6151, \"to\": 6155}, {\"ngram\": \"a criminal gang\", \"from\": 6168, \"to\": 6183}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 6204, \"to\": 6209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He and his brother Tristan Tate were also among the critics of this segment of the opening ceremony, andstood in front of a churchnear the French Embassy in Bucharest to protest.\", \"from\": 6213, \"to\": 6391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6232, \"end\": 6239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\", \"score\": 0.9999999919709808, \"rank\": 8.028789000715863e-09, \"text\": \"Tristan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\"}, {\"begin\": 6240, \"end\": 6244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\", \"score\": 0.9997170215751676, \"rank\": 0.0002829473240008194, \"text\": \"Tate\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\"}, {\"begin\": 6370, \"end\": 6379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bucharest\", \"score\": 0.9999999999868123, \"rank\": 1.3239499485746804e-11, \"text\": \"Bucharest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bucharest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bucharest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his brother\", \"from\": 6220, \"to\": 6231}, {\"ngram\": \"the critics\", \"from\": 6261, \"to\": 6272}, {\"ngram\": \"this segment\", \"from\": 6276, \"to\": 6288}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 6292, \"to\": 6312}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 6326, \"to\": 6331}, {\"ngram\": \"a churchnear\", \"from\": 6335, \"to\": 6347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Elon Musk also voiced his opinion, writing on X: \\\"Unless there is more bravery to stand up for what is fair and right, Christianity will perish,\\\" while Donald Trump also could not resist chipping in, describing the opening ceremony, and in particular the drag-queen sequence, as a \\\"disgrace\\\".\", \"from\": 6393, \"to\": 6685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6393, \"end\": 6402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elon Musk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\"}, {\"begin\": 6512, \"end\": 6524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999990248880046, \"rank\": 9.737873191006328e-07, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 6545, \"end\": 6557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999998252337872, \"rank\": 1.7475886385102696e-07, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his opinion\", \"from\": 6415, \"to\": 6426}, {\"ngram\": \"X\", \"from\": 6439, \"to\": 6440}, {\"ngram\": \"more bravery\", \"from\": 6459, \"to\": 6471}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 6604, \"to\": 6624}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"disgrace\", \"from\": 6672, \"to\": 6683}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am very open-minded, but I thought what they did was a disgrace,\\\" said the former US president in an interview with Fox News.\", \"from\": 6687, \"to\": 6815, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6772, \"end\": 6774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9977890766749423, \"rank\": 0.0022148019405816323, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 6806, \"end\": 6814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.783935572183626e-31, \"text\": \"Fox News\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a disgrace\", \"from\": 6743, \"to\": 6753}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 6788, \"to\": 6800}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ceremony's artistic director,Thomas Jolly, assured that the sequence was \\\"a great pagan festival linked to the gods of Olympus.\\\"\", \"from\": 6817, \"to\": 6949, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6850, \"end\": 6856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\", \"score\": 0.9999926918302319, \"rank\": 7.3081756036350455e-06, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\"}, {\"begin\": 6940, \"end\": 6947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\", \"score\": 0.9774302507714362, \"rank\": 0.023090905155981726, \"text\": \"Olympus\", \"types\": [\"Q8502\"], \"wikid\"